    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17530.0,
      "end_time": 20740.0,
      "text": "Before we move forward, though, let&#39;s review."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 20740.0,
      "end_time": 24280.0,
      "text": "Public corporations in Canada use IFRS, International"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 24280.0,
      "end_time": 26290.0,
      "text": "Financial Reporting Standards."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26290.0,
      "end_time": 29420.0,
      "text": "IFRS requires them to produce five statements-- the Income"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 29420.0,
