    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 36490.0,
      "end_time": 38590.0,
      "text": "Today we&#39;ll focus on the Statement of Financial"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38590.0,
      "end_time": 41230.0,
      "text": "Position, but let&#39;s review the previous statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 41230.0,
      "end_time": 42970.0,
      "text": "and the interconnection."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 42970.0,
      "end_time": 44780.0,
      "text": "The first financial statement produced"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 44780.0,
      "end_time": 46450.0,
      "text": "is the Income Statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 46450.0,
      "end_time": 49090.0,
      "text": "This statement measures a company&#39;s performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 49090.0,
      "end_time": 51670.0,
      "text": "The profit or loss from the Income Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 51670.0,
      "end_time": 53590.0,
      "text": "is used in multiple other statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 53590.0,
      "end_time": 55540.0,
      "text": "But right now, let&#39;s focus on the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 55540.0,
      "end_time": 57610.0,
      "text": "that the profit or loss is carried forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 57610.0,
      "end_time": 60310.0,
      "text": "to the Statement of Comprehensive Income."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 60310.0,
      "end_time": 63910.0,
      "text": "This statement adds or deducts unrealized gains or losses"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 63910.0,
      "end_time": 67390.0,
      "text": "to provide a broader definition of a company&#39;s performance, one"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 67390.0,
      "end_time": 70900.0,
      "text": "that includes both realized and unrealized amounts."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 70900.0,
      "end_time": 73480.0,
      "text": "The unrealized gains or losses on the Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 73480.0,
      "end_time": 76150.0,
      "text": "of Comprehensive Income are then carried forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 76150.0,
      "end_time": 78730.0,
      "text": "to the Statement of Changes in Equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 78730.0,
      "end_time": 81880.0,
      "text": "This statement reports how profits, dividends, shares,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 81880.0,
      "end_time": 84820.0,
      "text": "and other items have affected shareholders&#39; equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 84820.0,
      "end_time": 87130.0,
      "text": "Remember I said that the profit or loss from the Income"
