    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 87130.0,
      "end_time": 89950.0,
      "text": "Statement is used in multiple other statements?"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 89950.0,
      "end_time": 92800.0,
      "text": "You saw that it was used as the opening number in the Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 92800.0,
      "end_time": 94410.0,
      "text": "of Comprehensive Income."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 94410.0,
      "end_time": 97870.0,
      "text": "Here, it&#39;s used in the Retained Earnings column."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 97870.0,
      "end_time": 100450.0,
      "text": "The ending balances from the Statement of Changes in Equity"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 100450.0,
      "end_time": 102533.0,
      "text": "are then transferred to the Statement of Financial"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 102533.0,
      "end_time": 106160.0,
      "text": "Position, the subject of this video."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 106160.0,
      "end_time": 107660.0,
      "text": "The Statement of Financial Position"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107660.0,
      "end_time": 111200.0,
      "text": "summarizes the assets owned, the liabilities owed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 111200.0,
      "end_time": 113870.0,
      "text": "and the equity investment by the shareholders."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 113870.0,
      "end_time": 115820.0,
      "text": "This statement shows the financial health"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 115820.0,
      "end_time": 119239.0,
      "text": "of a company at a specific point in time."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 119239.0,
      "end_time": 121280.0,
      "text": "In order to understand the Statement of Financial"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 121280.0,
      "end_time": 123440.0,
      "text": "Position, we have to first understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 123440.0,
      "end_time": 126420.0,
      "text": "the elements that make up this statement-- assets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126420.0,
      "end_time": 128729.0,
      "text": "liabilities, and equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 128729.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131520.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s look at each individually."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 131520.0,
      "end_time": 133920.0,
      "text": "Everything that a company owns or controls"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 133920.0,
      "end_time": 136650.0,
      "text": "is considered an asset, a resource the company will"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 136650.0,
      "end_time": 138072.0,
      "text": "use in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 138072.0,
      "end_time": 140280.0,
      "text": "When you look at the assets, you answer the question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 140280.0,
      "end_time": 143520.0,
      "text": "what does the company have that they will use in the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 143520.0,
      "end_time": 145560.0,
      "text": "to help run the business?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 145560.0,
      "end_time": 147630.0,
      "text": "Assets are divided into two categories--"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 147630.0,
      "end_time": 150460.0,
      "text": "current and non-current or long-term."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 150460.0,
      "end_time": 151530.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 151530.0,
      "end_time": 153660.0,
      "text": "Financial statements are all about communicating"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 153660.0,
      "end_time": 156120.0,
      "text": "useful information to decision-makers"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 156120.0,
      "end_time": 159160.0,
      "text": "by grouping assets based on their characteristics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 159160.0,
      "end_time": 163350.0,
      "text": "in this case how fast they are used or converted into cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 163350.0,
      "end_time": 166020.0,
      "text": "Users obtain a better understanding of the company&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 166020.0,
      "end_time": 168330.0,
      "text": "financial position and health."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 168330.0,
      "end_time": 171930.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s define those two categories of assets."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 171930.0,
      "end_time": 173730.0,
      "text": "Current assets are any assets that"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 173730.0,
      "end_time": 175920.0,
      "text": "will be converted into cash, sold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 175920.0,
      "end_time": 179170.0,
      "text": "or consumed within one year or operating cycle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 179170.0,
      "end_time": 180900.0,
      "text": "whichever is longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 180900.0,
      "end_time": 182610.0,
      "text": "A few of the more common accounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 182610.0,
      "end_time": 184200.0,
      "text": "found in this grouping our things"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 184200.0,
      "end_time": 187230.0,
      "text": "like cash and prepaid expenses."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 187230.0,
      "end_time": 189510.0,
      "text": "Non-current assets are any assets"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 189510.0,
      "end_time": 192960.0,
      "text": "that do not meet the definition of a current asset."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 192960.0,
      "end_time": 195480.0,
      "text": "These are resources that will be converted into cash,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 195480.0,
      "end_time": 198760.0,
      "text": "sold, or used up over more than one year."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 198760.0,
      "end_time": 201240.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re divided into five subcategories--"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 201240.0,
      "end_time": 204150.0,
      "text": "long-term investments; property, plant, and equipment;"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 204150.0,
      "end_time": 207952.0,
      "text": "intangible assets; goodwill; and other assets."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 207952.0,
      "end_time": 209910.0,
      "text": "In order to better understand the accounts that"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 209910.0,
      "end_time": 212100.0,
      "text": "go into current and non-current assets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 212100.0,
      "end_time": 215100.0,
      "text": "I suggest you check out the Financial Statement Element"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 215100.0,
      "end_time": 218400.0,
      "text": "video which lists, defines, and describes"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 218400.0,
      "end_time": 221990.0,
      "text": "all the different accounts under each category."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 221990.0,
      "end_time": 224540.0,
      "text": "How do companies get their assets?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 224540.0,
      "end_time": 226310.0,
      "text": "They use liabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 226310.0,
      "end_time": 229800.0,
      "text": "Companies take on debt and owe third parties either money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 229800.0,
      "end_time": 231590.0,
      "text": "goods, or services."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 231590.0,
      "end_time": 233630.0,
      "text": "Like assets, liabilities are divided"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 233630.0,
      "end_time": 236660.0,
      "text": "into current and non-current, again to provide information"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 236660.0,
      "end_time": 239330.0,
      "text": "to users so they can make decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 239330.0,
      "end_time": 241100.0,
      "text": "Current liabilities are obligations"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 241100.0,
      "end_time": 244230.0,
      "text": "that will be satisfied in one year or operating cycle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 244230.0,
      "end_time": 245750.0,
      "text": "whichever is longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 245750.0,
      "end_time": 248630.0,
      "text": "Current liabilities include accounts such as accounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 248630.0,
      "end_time": 251350.0,
      "text": "payable and unearned revenue."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 251350.0,
      "end_time": 253440.0,
      "text": "Non-current, or long-term liabilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 253440.0,
      "end_time": 256839.0,
      "text": "are debts that will be satisfied beyond one year or operating"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 256839.0,
      "end_time": 259060.0,
      "text": "cycle, whichever is longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 259060.0,
      "end_time": 261220.0,
      "text": "Accounts included in this subcategory"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 261220.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264070.0,
      "text": "almost always have the word payable as part of the account"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 264070.0,
      "end_time": 265310.0,
      "text": "name."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 265310.0,
      "end_time": 268630.0,
      "text": "Again, to learn more, check out the Financial Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 268630.0,
      "end_time": 271090.0,
      "text": "Elements video which lists, defines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 271090.0,
      "end_time": 275140.0,
      "text": "and describes all the different accounts under each category."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 275140.0,
      "end_time": 277420.0,
      "text": "We already defined the element equity"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 277420.0,
      "end_time": 280090.0,
      "text": "when you completed the Statement of Changes in Equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 280090.0,
      "end_time": 282730.0,
      "text": "Equity is the financing by owners."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 282730.0,
      "end_time": 285020.0,
      "text": "Recall that it&#39;s made up of share capital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 285020.0,
      "end_time": 286540.0,
      "text": "retained earnings, and accumulated"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 286540.0,
      "end_time": 288340.0,
      "text": "other comprehensive income."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 288340.0,
      "end_time": 290740.0,
      "text": "It answers the question, what part of the business"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 290740.0,
      "end_time": 292720.0,
      "text": "is financed by the owners?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 292720.0,
      "end_time": 295600.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s just review the three items quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 295600.0,
      "end_time": 298420.0,
      "text": "Share capital represents the amount received in exchange"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 298420.0,
      "end_time": 299980.0,
      "text": "for company&#39;s shares."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 299980.0,
      "end_time": 302140.0,
      "text": "This is a direct investment by the shareholders"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 302140.0,
      "end_time": 304570.0,
      "text": "because shareholders choose to invest in the company"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 304570.0,
      "end_time": 306370.0,
      "text": "by buying shares."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 306370.0,
      "end_time": 309980.0,
      "text": "Next, the indirect investment called retained earnings."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 309980.0,
      "end_time": 311890.0,
      "text": "Retained earnings is increased by profit"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 311890.0,
      "end_time": 313540.0,
      "text": "and decreased by dividends paid out"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 313540.0,
      "end_time": 315310.0,
      "text": "to shareholders, as well as losses"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 315310.0,
      "end_time": 316900.0,
      "text": "from the Income Statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 316900.0,
      "end_time": 318520.0,
      "text": "The profit is kept in the business"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 318520.0,
      "end_time": 320870.0,
      "text": "to help them grow in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 320870.0,
      "end_time": 323830.0,
      "text": "Finally, accumulated other comprehensive income."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 323830.0,
      "end_time": 326610.0,
      "text": "This is the total of all unrealized gains and losses"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 326610.0,
      "end_time": 328360.0,
      "text": "from the Statement of Comprehensive Income"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 328360.0,
      "end_time": 330460.0,
      "text": "since the company began."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 330460.0,
      "end_time": 332920.0,
      "text": "This amount is increased by unrealized gains"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 332920.0,
      "end_time": 335810.0,
      "text": "and decreased by unrealized losses."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 335810.0,
      "end_time": 339510.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s do a quick check of your understanding so far."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 339510.0,
      "end_time": 342600.0,
      "text": "The right to receive money in the future from a customer"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 342600.0,
      "end_time": 343620.0,
      "text": "is an."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 349650.0,
      "end_time": 352320.0,
      "text": "Asset called accounts receivable."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 352320.0,
      "end_time": 354180.0,
      "text": "It is an asset because it will be converted"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 354180.0,
      "end_time": 357040.0,
      "text": "into cash in the future, and it has future economic benefit"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 357040.0,
      "end_time": 359770.0,
      "text": "for the company because it brings in cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 359770.0,
      "end_time": 361770.0,
      "text": "Now that we understand the elements that make up"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 361770.0,
      "end_time": 363270.0,
      "text": "the Statement of Financial Position,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 363270.0,
      "end_time": 365020.0,
      "text": "we can look at an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 365020.0,
      "end_time": 366540.0,
      "text": "Note that the statement is so large"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 366540.0,
      "end_time": 368370.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;ve divided it into sections so"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 368370.0,
      "end_time": 370770.0,
      "text": "that you can see them better."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 370770.0,
      "end_time": 373750.0,
      "text": "As always, the statement starts with the heading,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 373750.0,
      "end_time": 375960.0,
      "text": "which must include the company name and the title"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 375960.0,
      "end_time": 377640.0,
      "text": "of the financial statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 377640.0,
      "end_time": 380130.0,
      "text": "One change from previous statements-- the Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 380130.0,
      "end_time": 382950.0,
      "text": "of Financial Position is at a point in time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 382950.0,
      "end_time": 384970.0,
      "text": "not a period of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 384970.0,
      "end_time": 385950.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 385950.0,
      "end_time": 388450.0,
      "text": "Because every time a company has another transaction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 388450.0,
      "end_time": 390880.0,
      "text": "their financial position changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 390880.0,
      "end_time": 393360.0,
      "text": "For example, if you have $10 in your pocket"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 393360.0,
      "end_time": 397024.0,
      "text": "and then you buy a Timmy&#39;s, your financial position has changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 397024.0,
      "end_time": 398940.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why the Statement of Financial Position"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 398940.0,
      "end_time": 402330.0,
      "text": "is a snapshot, one second in time."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 402330.0,
      "end_time": 405150.0,
      "text": "The title of the statement reflects that."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 405150.0,
      "end_time": 406860.0,
      "text": "In this demonstration video, I&#39;ve"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 406860.0,
      "end_time": 408390.0,
      "text": "followed the common North American"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 408390.0,
      "end_time": 411930.0,
      "text": "practice of listing current items before non-current items."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 411930.0,
      "end_time": 414360.0,
      "text": "This is called order of liquidity."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 414360.0,
      "end_time": 416500.0,
      "text": "The order is current assets before"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 416500.0,
      "end_time": 418650.0,
      "text": "non-current and current liabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 418650.0,
      "end_time": 421020.0,
      "text": "before non-current liabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 421020.0,
      "end_time": 423180.0,
      "text": "Although I have set up the statement in columns"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 423180.0,
      "end_time": 425220.0,
      "text": "for easy viewing, the accounts can all"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 425220.0,
      "end_time": 428490.0,
      "text": "be listed in one column and the amounts in another."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 428490.0,
      "end_time": 431520.0,
      "text": "Here you see the details of the Current Asset section."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 431520.0,
      "end_time": 434310.0,
      "text": "Notice that the assets are listed in order of liquidity."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 434310.0,
      "end_time": 437850.0,
      "text": "The faster I convert them into cash, sell, or use them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 437850.0,
      "end_time": 439840.0,
      "text": "the higher they are on the list."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 439840.0,
      "end_time": 443990.0,
      "text": "Note that there is a subtotal called total current assets."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 443990.0,
      "end_time": 447020.0,
      "text": "The next section is the Non-current Assets."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 447020.0,
      "end_time": 449180.0,
      "text": "I have listed them from long-term investment"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 449180.0,
      "end_time": 450440.0,
      "text": "to goodwill."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 450440.0,
      "end_time": 453170.0,
      "text": "Notice, if there is only one item in the section,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 453170.0,
      "end_time": 455630.0,
      "text": "there is no subtotal necessary."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 455630.0,
      "end_time": 459440.0,
      "text": "Intangibles and goodwill are examples of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 459440.0,
      "end_time": 462055.0,
      "text": "If there are more than one item listed under a heading,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 462055.0,
      "end_time": 464180.0,
      "text": "as there is for long-term investments and property,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 464180.0,
      "end_time": 468020.0,
      "text": "plant, and equipment, there must be a subtotal."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 468020.0,
      "end_time": 470050.0,
      "text": "The next section is called Liabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 470050.0,
      "end_time": 471770.0,
      "text": "and Shareholders&#39; Equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 471770.0,
      "end_time": 473870.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve started with current liabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 473870.0,
      "end_time": 475900.0,
      "text": "and provided a subtotal before moving on"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 475900.0,
      "end_time": 477830.0,
      "text": "to non-current liabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 477830.0,
      "end_time": 481130.0,
      "text": "Note, each section has its own subtotal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 481130.0,
      "end_time": 484550.0,
      "text": "and then total liabilities is provided at the bottom."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 484550.0,
      "end_time": 487310.0,
      "text": "The accounts within current and non-current liabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 487310.0,
      "end_time": 489890.0,
      "text": "are an order of when they will be settled."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 489890.0,
      "end_time": 493550.0,
      "text": "The earlier they&#39;re settled, the higher they are on the listing."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 493550.0,
      "end_time": 495920.0,
      "text": "The final section is Shareholders&#39; Equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 495920.0,
      "end_time": 498470.0,
      "text": "Notice that the order of shareholders&#39; equity items--"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 498470.0,
      "end_time": 501050.0,
      "text": "common shares, retained earnings, and accumulated"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 501050.0,
      "end_time": 502520.0,
      "text": "other comprehensive income--"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 502520.0,
      "end_time": 505100.0,
      "text": "are the same as the order of the columns in the Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 505100.0,
      "end_time": 506600.0,
      "text": "of Changes in Equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 506600.0,
      "end_time": 508730.0,
      "text": "There is a subtotal for shareholders&#39; equity"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 508730.0,
      "end_time": 510980.0,
      "text": "before total liabilities and shareholders&#39; equity"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 510980.0,
      "end_time": 512600.0,
      "text": "is provided."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 512600.0,
      "end_time": 515059.0,
      "text": "Notice something really important."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 515058.99999999994,
      "end_time": 517788.99999999994,
      "text": "Total assets are equal to total liabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 517789.0,
      "end_time": 519200.0,
      "text": "plus shareholders&#39; equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 519200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522090.00000000006,
      "text": "This is called the accounting equation."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 522090.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524630.0,
      "text": "This equation shows that economic resources--"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 524630.0,
      "end_time": 527990.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s our assets-- are financed either through debt"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 527990.0,
      "end_time": 531170.0,
      "text": "or liabilities or equity from shareholders."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 531170.0,
      "end_time": 534020.0,
      "text": "This equation will be explored in a later video."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 534020.0,
      "end_time": 536264.0,
      "text": "For now, it&#39;s important to recognize"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 536264.0,
      "end_time": 537680.0,
      "text": "that in the Statement of Financial"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 537680.0,
      "end_time": 540350.0,
      "text": "Position assets always equals liabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 540350.0,
      "end_time": 543120.0,
      "text": "plus shareholders&#39; equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 543120.0,
      "end_time": 545390.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s check your understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 545390.0,
      "end_time": 547520.0,
      "text": "Shareholders&#39; equity is always placed"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 547520.0,
      "end_time": 550010.0,
      "text": "after liabilities on the Statement of Financial Position"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 550010.0,
      "end_time": 550590.0,
      "text": "under IFRS."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 556350.0,
      "end_time": 559440.0,
      "text": "You likely said true, but the correct answer"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 559440.0,
      "end_time": 561110.0,
      "text": "is actually false."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 561110.0,
      "end_time": 564570.0,
      "text": "IFRS allows choice with regards to the order of the categories"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 564570.0,
      "end_time": 566830.0,
      "text": "on the Statement of Financial Position."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 566830.0,
      "end_time": 568680.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s common in North America to use"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 568680.0,
      "end_time": 570390.0,
      "text": "order of liquidity, which is what"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 570390.0,
      "end_time": 573210.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve used in the statements I demonstrated."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 573210.0,
      "end_time": 576390.0,
      "text": "More common for international and European corporations"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 576390.0,
      "end_time": 578490.0,
      "text": "is reverse liquidity order."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 578490.0,
      "end_time": 580500.0,
      "text": "On these statements, non-current assets"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 580500.0,
      "end_time": 583200.0,
      "text": "are listed first, then current assets."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 583200.0,
      "end_time": 585090.0,
      "text": "In addition, shareholders&#39; equity is actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 585090.0,
      "end_time": 587760.0,
      "text": "listed before liabilities, and liabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 587760.0,
      "end_time": 589620.0,
      "text": "are in reverse order, meaning that it&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 589620.0,
      "end_time": 593470.0,
      "text": "non-current liabilities before current liabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 593470.0,
      "end_time": 595150.0,
      "text": "Within each category, the accounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 595150.0,
      "end_time": 597160.0,
      "text": "are also listed in reverse order."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 597160.0,
      "end_time": 599380.0,
      "text": "That means that under current assets"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 599380.0,
      "end_time": 603040.0,
      "text": "cash would be last, not first."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 603040.0,
      "end_time": 605920.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s important to understand that IFRS provides choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 605920.0,
      "end_time": 608200.0,
      "text": "But for purposes of these videos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 608200.0,
      "end_time": 610600.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll continue to use order of liquidity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 610600.0,
      "end_time": 613820.0,
      "text": "which is most common in North American companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 613820.0,
      "end_time": 616630.0,
      "text": "So what questions does the Statement of Financial Position"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 616630.0,
      "end_time": 617680.0,
      "text": "answer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 617680.0,
      "end_time": 619810.0,
      "text": "For investors, it shows that the company"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 619810.0,
      "end_time": 621940.0,
      "text": "can repay its current and non-current debt"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 621940.0,
      "end_time": 623350.0,
      "text": "as they come due."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 623350.0,
      "end_time": 625330.0,
      "text": "For creditors, it indicates if there&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 625330.0,
      "end_time": 627370.0,
      "text": "enough assets to operate."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 627370.0,
      "end_time": 629800.0,
      "text": "If they can&#39;t operate, is there enough assets"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 629800.0,
      "end_time": 632950.0,
      "text": "to cover outstanding debts when they&#39;re sold?"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 632950.0,
      "end_time": 634390.0,
      "text": "Does the company have enough cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 634390.0,
      "end_time": 636730.0,
      "text": "to pay its debts as they come due?"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 636730.0,
      "end_time": 640570.0,
      "text": "Considering current debt levels, should we lend them more money?"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 640570.0,
      "end_time": 642370.0,
      "text": "For both investors and lenders, it"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 642370.0,
      "end_time": 646210.0,
      "text": "answers the question, what does the company use, debt or equity"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 646210.0,
      "end_time": 647840.0,
      "text": "financing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 647840.0,
      "end_time": 649650.0,
      "text": "The Statement of Financial Position"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 649650.0,
      "end_time": 651480.0,
      "text": "is not the last financial statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 651480.0,
      "end_time": 653070.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to complete."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 653070.0,
      "end_time": 655710.0,
      "text": "The numbers from this statement, particularly the amount"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 655710.0,
      "end_time": 660240.0,
      "text": "of cash, are used in the Statement of Cash Flows, which"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 660240.0,
      "end_time": 663330.0,
      "text": "is the topic of our next video."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 663330.0,
      "end_time": 666080.0,
      "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]"
    }
  ]
}